summary: Finished Spider-Man PS4 earlier. REALLY good game. Liked the teases for a possible sequel at the end. =D Still need to play the...
body:
Finished Spider-Man PS4 earlier. REALLY good game. Liked the teases for a possible sequel at the end. =D Still need to play the DLC episodes, though.

I wonder if Insomniac or Rocksteady could work on a Superman or Wonder Woman game, eventually? They’ve done good work on this and Batman, respectively, and I think a game for those two by either of company would be great to see.

summary: So I did eventually go and see Spider-verse with some college friends and oh my LORD I am in love with the characters, the...
caption:
So I did eventually go and see Spider-verse with some college friends and oh my LORD I am in love with the characters, the animation style and just the creative story it tells! The time and effort that went into that movie is phenomenal! Mind blowing! If you haven’t seen the movie I highly recommend you to watch it! Even just the little details in the animation style just made the whole movie incredible - like you know how comic books, or old ones, were drawn using tiny coloured dots - they added that affect into the animation, the animators didn’t HAVE to do that! But they DID! Its honestly one of the greatest movies I’ve seen and it quickly became one of my favourites!

So I’ve been debating on if I should do a spider sona or not, as much as I love spider man I’m not a die hard fan so I don’t know all the details of the spider man movies - but after seeing so many cool and unique spider sona characters on Twitter I finally caved in and made my own! She was actually really fun to draw, like Spider Gwen I wanted her to have really elegant like legs but I wanted to give her a more strudy like build, hence the wider hips. 

Also can I just add that I F*CKING LOVE GWEN!! Her spider women outfit is gorgeous!! I know the movie focuses on Miles and how he becomes spider man in his universe, but I think Gwen has taken first place for my favourite character from that movie (Also side note I love the fact that Gwen still wears her ballet shoes even while fighting, me and a friend joked about how Gwen would elegantly kick bad guys with excellent ballet posture)

Hope you guys like my spider sona!
